**Now many people have a question, but what exactly is the value of these fragments?** Many people will think that this is a pointless experiment from which nothing will come, but in fact everything is much more serious.

I would like to start by saying that thanks to this experiment, we have a **unique** opportunity to come together and create a **closed community** üîí that will develop through joint efforts.

To achieve this goal, it is necessary that the majority of holders decide to "hold" the gift. At the moment, it is not clear how many people are really ready to "hold" and support the formation of a community. 

Since the start of the experiment, more than **200** fragments have already been resold. The number of holders increased by about **35-40%**. Some of the holders who managed to buy the fragment at the start decided to made **x2.5 - 3** and leave this project. **Was it the right decision on their part? Unlikely.**

The flora on the Green Heart Locket is now **1400TON**üíé
There is no need to make a decision to "sell", because there will be no benefit from this ‚ùå. Instead, it's worth joining forces and starting to buy back fragments that are sold by those who do not see value in the future of this project. **Only we, the holders, can create value for a closed club if we act together and coherently.**

Congratulations to all those who bought the fragments during the start of sales! You got a chance to stay in a **closed club** and the opportunity to get really worthwhile networking, which will be formed as the club develops.

In order to form a community faster, it was decided to create the "**heart of the club** üíù" - a separate wallet and account that will store fragments and constantly vote for the "hold" gift, so that the club will exist forever.

==========================================================
**FAQ:**
**‚Ä¢ How can I chat if my fragment is stored in the heart of the club?**
__- If you have several fragments, you can send some fragments to the heart of the club, **but you must have at least one fragment in your wallet**.__‚ùóÔ∏è

**‚Ä¢ Why would I send fragments to the heart of the club?**
__- No one obliges you to send them. If you support the idea of forming a closed club and realize the value that it will have in the future, then you can send fragments to the club's strategic reserve. If anything happens, these fragments will be returned to the club members in the future, and if the person leaves the club earlier, his fragments will be "**burned**".__

**‚Ä¢ I do not want to send my fragments, but I am ready to help in the development of the club. What can I do?**
__- In addition to sending your fragments to the heart of the club, you can send a **TON**üíé, which will be used to redeem the fragments. Even if **30%** of the holders send 0.5 **TON**üíé each, then at the moment it will be possible to buy out **1%** of the salary, which will help maintain the minimum price for joining the club. **Thus, the cost of admission to the club will only increase**__ __üí∏__

**‚Ä¢ What if there are extra TONüíé in the heart of the club?**
__- In this case, we will take a collective opinion on where to invest this money and for how long. After that, we will be able to split this profit equally.__

‚Ä¢ Which wallet can I send my fragments or **TON**üíé to‚ùî
